  "section": "2",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Alchemy_Equipment\">Alchemy Equipment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Oblivion:Miscellaneous_Items&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Alchemy Equipment\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Grade</th>\n<th>ID\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-icon-Weight.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/3/3a/OB-icon-Weight.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-icon-Value.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/5/50/OB-icon-Value.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Oblivion:Alchemy#Strength_of_Apparatus\" title=\"Oblivion:Alchemy\">Strength</a>\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-icon-misc-Alembic.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"OB-icon-misc-Alembic.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/00/OB-icon-misc-Alembic.png/48px-OB-icon-misc-Alembic.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/0/00/OB-icon-misc-Alembic.png 1.5x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\"><span id=\"Alembic\"></span>Alembic\n</td>\n<td>Novice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">010604</span></span></span></td>\n<td>7.0</td>\n<td>50</td>\n<td>0.1\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">Decreases the magnitude of all negative effects in <a href=\"/wiki/Oblivion:Alchemy\" title=\"Oblivion:Alchemy\">Alchemy</a>.<br />\n<p><i>(When brewing a Poison [i.e. a Potion with only negative effects], the Alembic will have the opposite effect, increasing negative effects and durations.)</i>\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Apprentice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06E310</span></span></span></td>\n<td>7.25</td>\n<td>100</td>\n<td>0.25\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Journeyman</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE52</span></span></span></td>\n<td>7.5</td>\n<td>250</td>\n<td>0.5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Expert</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE5C</span></span></span></td>\n<td>7.75</td>\n<td>500</td>\n<td>0.75\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Master</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE64</span></span></span></td>\n<td>8.0</td>\n<td>1000</td>\n<td>1.0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-icon-misc-Calcinator.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"OB-icon-misc-Calcinator.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/80/OB-icon-misc-Calcinator.png/48px-OB-icon-misc-Calcinator.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/8/80/OB-icon-misc-Calcinator.png 1.5x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\"><span id=\"Calcinator\"></span>Calcinator\n</td>\n<td>Novice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">01057D</span></span></span></td>\n<td>5.0</td>\n<td>50</td>\n<td>0.1\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">Increases the magnitude of ALL effects in Alchemy.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Apprentice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06E311</span></span></span></td>\n<td>5.25</td>\n<td>100</td>\n<td>0.25\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Journeyman</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE55</span></span></span></td>\n<td>5.5</td>\n<td>250</td>\n<td>0.5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Expert</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE5E</span></span></span></td>\n<td>5.75</td>\n<td>500</td>\n<td>0.75\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Master</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE66</span></span></span></td>\n<td>6.0</td>\n<td>1000</td>\n<td>1.0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"6\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-icon-misc-MortarAndPestle.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"OB-icon-misc-MortarAndPestle.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/65/OB-icon-misc-MortarAndPestle.png/48px-OB-icon-misc-MortarAndPestle.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/6/65/OB-icon-misc-MortarAndPestle.png 1.5x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"6\"><span id=\"Mortar_.26_Pestle\"></span>Mortar &amp; Pestle\n</td>\n<td><i>Novice</i></td>\n<td><i><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">0C7968</span></span></span></i></td>\n<td><i>1.0</i></td>\n<td><i>25</i></td>\n<td><i>0.1</i>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"6\">Required tool for all Alchemy.<br /><i>(The first one is the one you get during the <a href=\"/wiki/Oblivion:Tutorial\" title=\"Oblivion:Tutorial\">tutorial</a>. The only difference is a script that makes a tutorial message appear the first time you pick it up. Also, it won't stack with other Novice Mortar &amp; Pestles.)</i><br />A <a href=\"/wiki/Shivering:Mixing_Bowl\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shivering:Mixing Bowl\">Mixing Bowl</a> is the equivalent of an Apprentice Mortar and Pestle and can be found in the <a href=\"/wiki/Shivering:Shivering_Isles\" title=\"Shivering:Shivering Isles\">Shivering Isles</a>.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Novice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">0105E3</span></span></span></td>\n<td>1.0</td>\n<td>25</td>\n<td>0.1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Apprentice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06E312</span></span></span></td>\n<td>1.25</td>\n<td>75</td>\n<td>0.25\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Journeyman</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE57</span></span></span></td>\n<td>1.5</td>\n<td>250</td>\n<td>0.5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Expert</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE60</span></span></span></td>\n<td>1.75</td>\n<td>500</td>\n<td>0.75\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Master</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE68</span></span></span></td>\n<td>2.0</td>\n<td>1000</td>\n<td>1.0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-icon-misc-Retort.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"OB-icon-misc-Retort.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/a6/OB-icon-misc-Retort.png/48px-OB-icon-misc-Retort.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/a/a6/OB-icon-misc-Retort.png 1.5x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\"><span id=\"Retort\"></span>Retort\n</td>\n<td>Novice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">000C4F</span></span></span></td>\n<td>3.0</td>\n<td>50</td>\n<td>0.1\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">Increases the magnitude and duration of all positive effects in Alchemy.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Apprentice</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06E313</span></span></span></td>\n<td>3.25</td>\n<td>100</td>\n<td>0.25\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Journeyman</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE59</span></span></span></td>\n<td>3.5</td>\n<td>250</td>\n<td>0.5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Expert</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE62</span></span></span></td>\n<td>3.75</td>\n<td>500</td>\n<td>0.75\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Master</td>\n<td><span class=\"idall\"><span class=\"idref\">00<span class=\"idcase\">06EE6A</span></span></span></td>\n<td>4.0</td>\n<td>1000</td>\n<td>1.0\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<dl><dd><table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Apparatus Quality Level</th>\n<th>Vendors sell to Character Level</th>\n<th>Dungeon loot at Character Level\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Novice</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Apprentice</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Journeyman</td>\n<td>14</td>\n<td>9\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Expert</td>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>13\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Master</td>\n<td><i>Never</i></td>\n<td>17\n</td></tr></tbody></table></dd></dl>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-nolines\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 205px\"><div style=\"width: 205px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-item-Alembic.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f5/OB-item-Alembic.png/199px-OB-item-Alembic.png\" width=\"199\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f5/OB-item-Alembic.png/298px-OB-item-Alembic.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f5/OB-item-Alembic.png/398px-OB-item-Alembic.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>Alembics\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 205px\"><div style=\"width: 205px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-item-Calcinator.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/4f/OB-item-Calcinator.png/200px-OB-item-Calcinator.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"174\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/4f/OB-item-Calcinator.png/300px-OB-item-Calcinator.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/4/4f/OB-item-Calcinator.png/400px-OB-item-Calcinator.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>Calcinators\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 205px\"><div style=\"width: 205px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 200px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:OB-item-Mortar_and_Pestle.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/OB-item-Mortar_and_Pestle.png/200px-OB-item-Mortar_and_Pestle.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/OB-item-Mortar_and_Pestle.png/300px-OB-item-Mortar_and_Pestle.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/OB-item-Mortar_and_Pestle.png/400px-OB-item-Mortar_a